reviews.review_text: Good staff, went out of theyre way to make sure my needs were met. Great job Staff.
Thank you Divya for the great service and support. He is a great guy . Once again Thank you so much for a great service.
They have a great selection here and staff is very friendly
Great place to pick up all your winter spring summer and fall clothes. I do.

Had an issue with a staff member 2 find my pick up  on-line order near closing time & she just went home & left me standing there  , last staff member quickly grabbed my order after closing time, long story short after raising my complaint with management he went above & beyond my expectations.  . Great after sales service & top quality products at Marks, been a customer 4 over 20 years.
Staff are excellent! Prices are a bit too expensive on some products!

Bought my steel toe shoes here. I looked on their website first to see stock options. My closest store did not have my choice in stock however the clerk was kind enough she called another store to put a hold on my size. Good CS but FYI stock gets quickly bought up.

I had ordered a couple of items online, but one didnt fit so I returned it. The returns process was very easy and because I was at the store right at opening, it was not crowded at all. I did a little browsing and found a couple of items that I liked. The store was well kept and well stocked, and the clerks were very pleasant and helpful.

The staff were super friendly. They knew exactly what they were doing and selling. The store was very organized, clean, well stocked. I came in there just in time because they were having a great sale and I got my moneys worth. I enjoyed every single minute I was there. I am not sucking up I am just being honest.
5 star ratings for both the female sales associate and the male supervisor who helped me on Dec 10, 2021 Friday evening. They were very accommodating and patient in handling my return.
Not many staff to help, but prices are good, and quality is good.

I Always find what I am looking for.  Great quality with a good price, and now that I can use my Canadian tire money even better! If you are looking for good deals, check often, the clearance section is a must, I found for my husband a pair of Clarks and the price was beyond my expectations. I always buy my working shoes in here because I am never disappointed
This was my 1st time at this Marks. Nice store, large selections for both men & women. Staff were quite friendly...! Reasonable prices. Definitely will go back.
During Covid 19 ordering online can be a hassle. Does not seem to be a problem with Marks - ordered it one day, it arrived the next. AWESOME company, FANTASTIC products, OUTSTANDING service

Excellent customer service. I had an issue I thought may not get resolved (a pair of steel toed boots that didnt seem to be in my size as there was a size up and a size down in the same box) but the individual helping me went above and beyond to find my size nestled way in the back.
